</div>
		<div>The visual style I used for redesigning the concept of the page is mainly focused on simplicity. After analyzing the different types of elements that Bunq offers across the website I realized the style is based on a very fun, flat and simple design. Therefore, I created a few icons that follow these principles and emphasize the main concept. These also ensure better access to achieve a more inclusive user experience. Especially the full icons will make the interface easier recognizable for people that are visually impaired. I worked on the visual style while following a very similar font and color palette that resembles the actual Bunq-website.
</div>
