</div>
		<div>The first thing I noticed while inspecting the website was the amount of information that can be classified into more concise and easy accessible categories that will bring the user faster to his/her destination on the website. Therefore, I redesigned the main menu following the main categories the user would need quick access to.
</div>
		<div>make itÂ simple.useful.clear.</div>
		<div>For the second part of the page, I decided it was very important to show the actual story paragraph, followed by the values that make the brand human. I also decided to add interactive transitions. This makes sure the user stays focused, especially those with a short attention span.
</div>
		<div>our story</div>
		<div>The main objective of creating an 'about us page' is to showcase the brand's services and personality. For that reason, I chose to make use of the great introduction video the other channels offer. It has a modern feeling and makes the site interactive, dynamic and approachable in many ways. In my opinion it's important to also use this visual aspect on the about page since Bunq is a relatively new brand that currently is positioning itself in the market. This means visitors might tend to show a specific interest in the about page.
</div>
